lead_paragraph: Danuel House scored 19 points and No. 20 Texas A&M rolled off 20 straight in a come-from-behind 81-63 victory over Auburn on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 20 Texas A&M Races to 81-63 Win Over Auburn
